 And then we basically create a simple form, we're gonna post to the login URL, that just looks up the login URL, and we've got this context variable called form, and we can print that out, that form has the key, that form has all of the input stuff in it, we're gonna talk about forms coming up soon, and so that's what generates, this form here generates all this stuff right here, and so there could be a bunch of things in there.

