 So I've been talking about a view that requires a logged in user, and so again, imagine something where you're sort of reading your messages on an online system, and you bookmark the message reading URL, and then you shut your browser down, which logs you out of the system, and then you click on that bookmark straight to the messages, my inbox or whatever, and then inbox looks at you and says you're not logged in, so I'm gonna send you to log in, you finish logging in, and then you come back, that's what the next equals does.

